						<summary>

						<p>Registers a sale of land (<hi rend="italic">tirumaḍaippaḷḷipuṟam</hi>) to a certain <hi rend="bold">Brahmamārājar.</hi> The record is dated <hi rend="bold">Kaṭaka, Śu. 3, Wednesday, Maghā</hi> in the <hi rend="bold">10th year</hi> of the king's reign, corresponding to A.D. <hi rend="bold">1127, July 13, Wednesday,</hi> f.d.t. ·20; ·51.</p>						

